Class FacultyDAOHibImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • in.co.sunrays.proj0.dao.FacultyDAOHibImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    FacultyDAOInt

    @Repository
public class FacultyDAOHibImpl
extends java.lang.Object
implements FacultyDAOInt
    Faculty Data Access Object provides Database CRUD operations. It is implemented by plain Hibernate 3 API with Spring ORM. All methods propagate unchecked DataAccessException. It is a generic exception handling provided by Spring-DAO. If DataAccessException is propagated from method then declarative transaction is rolled back by Spring AOP. This is plain Hibernate 3 API implementation of DAO
